edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.ontology

Class Entity

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.harvard.hms.dbmi.bd2k.irct.model.ontology.Entity

  • @Entity
public class Entity
extends java.lang.Object
    The Entity class represents a path, and object in a resource. Entities can be linked to other paths through ontology relationships.
    Author:
    Jeremy R. Easton-Marks
